rows.label: qev041605_MSG0002
rows.name:
Who knows where that which Bobora seeks lies?
Only stars above.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0003
rows.name: Hmm? Friend needs something from Bobora?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0004
rows.name:
It must be important for friend to interrupt deep
spiritual conversation between Bobora and stars.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0005
rows.name:
...Huh? Nopon courier was attacked by huge something
or other and had cargo stolen?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0006
rows.name: That have nothing to do with Bobora.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0007
rows.name:
...Except for the part where Bobora saw entire
thing go down from here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0008
rows.name:
It was giant bird that attacked the courier.
They call it jacul ire.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0009
rows.name:
It live around these parts, but is pretty rare.
At first glance, it look like auravis.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0010
rows.name:
Part of body of jacul ire covered in mushroom-looking
things. Also, it attack with spore-ish junk.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0011
rows.name: Still, it hardly ever show up around other living things...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0012
rows.name:
But this mating season.
Maybe that why it looked so agitated.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0013
rows.name:
After it took cargo, it flew off to...
Hmm. From this angle, it look like it flew south.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0014
rows.name:
Bobora may not be able to find what Bobora
looking for, but always been good with directions.
Knowing how to ask the stars helps.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0015
rows.name: Jacul ire that stole cargo definitely flew south![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0016
rows.name:
Hmm? Friend is back. Does friend have terrible sense
of direction?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0017
rows.name: Jacul ire flew to the south![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0018
rows.name:
Bobora not know anything past that.
Bobora busy enough dealing with own biz.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041605_MSG0019
rows.name: Freight of courier no concern of Bobora.[ST:wait ]
